PEOPLE: NATION 
* Norman S. Matthews, former president of Federated Department Stores, will be 
named a director of Best Products Co., New York, and will serve as vice 
chairman. Matthews will assume these positions immediately after the completion 
of the merger of Best Products and BAC Acquisition Corp., the company formed by 
Adler &amp; Shaykin for the leveraged buyout of Best Products. 
